## What is SteemDesk?

SteemDesk is an existing project which provides missing tools for Steemit users. This includes the ability to delegate Steem Power.

## How do I create a SteemDesk account?

You cannot create an account on StemDesk, but you can insert your Steemit.com username to use the available tools on SteemDesk.
 
## What is Steemit?

Steemit is a social networking and blogging site on the Steem blockchain. The Steem blockchain rewards user's blog posts, videos, and other contributions in the cryptocurrencies STEEM and SBD.  

## What is the relationship between SteemDesk and Steemit.com?

SteemDesk is a collections of tools associated with Steemit; such as view accounts activity, delegation of Steem Power. More features will be addes in the future.

## What is Steem?

Steem is a blockchain-based social media platform where anyone can earn rewards. The Steem blockchain not only holds a cryptocurrency token called STEEM, but also content created by its users, a system to vote on that content, and many other features you would find on popular social networking sites

## What are the missing tools to delegate SP?

SteemDesk also provides tools to delegate SP through the website. The SP delegation goes directly to the target account. Just enter the amount and the username.

## Where can I leave feedback, suggestions, or report bugs?

[Please, use the project's GitHub issue page.](https://github.com/cutemachine/SteemDesk/issues)
